t: "Has not the story come to them about those who preceded them, NoahÂṀs folk, and AdÂṀs and ThamiidÂṀs, and AbrahamÂṀs folk and the inhabitants of Midian and the Overthrown [Towns]? Their messengers brought them clear explanations; it was not God Who injured them, but they themselves who inflicted the injury"